    p Don’t cache or store data you receive via the Minihero API for an unreasonable amount of time given the relevance of that data and how it is used on your application.
    p Protect any keys used to access the Minihero API and any data you receive via the Minihero API against unauthorized access, use or disclosure, and immediately report security issues to api_license@minihero.org.
    p Clearly indicate in the application that the application uses the Minihero API but is not verified by Minihero, Inc.
